{
  "stem": "8212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I thought it was marvelous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I really enjoyed being with the young people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The parents were not at all happy, but we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, somehow young people always kind of can do it, can get over this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after a few months of this camp, somehow we found out, my parents found out, that France-- that they are going to send these people to another camp, which was much worse.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So again, we escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We escaped, and we went live in Lyon, which is a city in the middle of France.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there, again, we lived in terrible conditions in a very small place in a bad part of the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But-- it was terrible, but on the other hand, there were always people like us, people that came from Vienna, people that had wonderful backgrounds.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we kind of always got together, and we knew-- we were hoping that it was a temporary thing, that it was not getting worse.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So you could take it because of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were in Lyon, I think, from 1941 'til 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My sister went to school, and I-- at this point, I think was 13 or 14-- I was always interested in art since I was a little girl in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Whenever I went to see my grandparents on Sunday, they used to have invitations for weddings and things, very beautiful paper.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was very bored, so I used to draw women with dresses with little dogs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I used to draw them-- I used to draw the person in front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the legs were always in profile, like the Egyptians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't know how to do perspective.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So that's how I drew, one after the other, ideas, fashion.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
